         <div type="writingSession" n="1"> 
            <p> 
               <date when="19040707" n="1">7/7</date> Leichenbegängnis <rs type="person" ref="pmb11673">Theodor Herzl</rs>. Schöner Sommertag. Sprach <rs type="person" ref="pmb2992">Rotenstern</rs> (<rs type="place" ref="pmb174">russ.</rs> Übersetzungen) <rs type="person" ref="pmb12772">Servaes</rs>, dann draußen <rs type="person" ref="pmb10815">Bahr</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pmb12968">Trebitsch</rs> (der Mittwoch <rs type="person" ref="pmb11673">Herzl</rs> in <rs type="place" ref="pmb470"> 
                  <settlement>Edlach</settlement> 
               </rs> besucht hatte. Als die Sonne unterging, sagte <rs type="person" ref="pmb11673">Herzl</rs> 
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/> 
               <c rendition="#dots" n="3" place="center"/> 
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/> 
               <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KD231-2">Le soir <c rendition="#dots" n="3" place="center"/> mon soir, bon soir</anchor>).– <rs type="person" ref="pmb2167">Salten</rs> 
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>u. a.– Die Zionisten.– <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KD231-1">Mit <rs type="person" ref="pmb10815">Bahr</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="pmb12968">Treb.</rs> zurück;</anchor> 
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/> 
               <rs type="person" ref="pmb12968">Trebitsch</rs> noch bei mir am Balkon.–</p> 
            <p>Nm. dictirt <rs type="work" subtype="implied" ref="pmb29923">Roman</rs>, aphoristisches.–</p> 
            <p>Abd. mit <rs type="person" ref="pmb2173">O.</rs> 
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/> 
               <rs type="person" ref="pmb2315">Liesl</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pmb12837">Steinrück</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="pmb8">Prater</rs>: Constantinhügel, Wurstel, Rutschbahn etc.–</p> 
         </div> 
